1.name: Dorra
1.desc: A basic currency that can be used in various features.
1.literary: Issued by Deepsea Finance, this currency circulates throughout Nova Continent ... but only within cities.If you're alone in the Wilds, all the Dorra you carry might as well be scrap paper.

2.name: Stellanite Dust
2.desc: A rare crystal that can be exchanged for vouchers in the Shop.
2.literary: This shard vibrates with the power of Stellnanite Veins, exhibiting purity yet bearing the hallmarks of human craftsmanship.Though not as pristine as natural crystals, it holds immense value.

3.name: Stellanite Lumina
3.desc: An extremely rare crystal of immense value.
3.literary: A condensed mass imbued with the power of Stellnanite Vein, both hard and clear.For centuries, it has been revered as the material for crafting Soul Stones, carrying immense value.

4.name: Stellanite Lumina
4.desc: An extremely rare crystal of immense value.
4.literary: A condensed mass imbued with the power of Stellnanite Vein, both hard and clear.For centuries, it has been revered as the material for crafting Soul Stones, carrying immense value.

11.name: Stella Coin
11.desc: The currency used for purchases within the Monolith.
11.literary: A coin that gleams with starlight, exclusive to the Monolith.Spend it while you can; you can't bring it out anyway.

12.name: Journey Ticket
12.desc: A reward obtained after completing the Monolith. Can be exchanged for items in the Shop.
12.literary: Obtained at the end of the exploration journey, this commemorative ticket stub symbolizes the honor of scaling the heights.Yet, for many Trekkers, a clear head and safe return are far more cherished than any accolades.

20.name: Vigor
20.desc: Stamina used for engaging in various game modes.
20.literary: Taking on commissions and completing quests becomes doubly hard without enthusiasm.Don't forget to pep up your Trekkers before embarking on your journey!

21.name: EXP
21.desc: Proof of the Tyrant's influence on the world. Increases your Authorization Level.
21.literary: The Throne system requires a certain amount of EXP. Increase your Authorization Level to unlock more features.

22.name: Grant Tier
22.desc: A proof of your activity in the Startup Grant. Used to level up the Grant Tier.
22.literary: As you explore the Monolith and beyond, the Startup Grant will amplify your progress, making every step count double.

23.name: Travel Permit
23.desc: A certificate obtained through recruiting Trekkers. Can be exchanged for items in the Shop.
23.literary: A testament to every distant voyage,where each stack's thickness whispers tales of delightful encounters.

24.name: Expert Permit
24.desc: A certificate obtained through recruiting Trekkers. Can be exchanged for rare items in the Shop.
24.literary: A testament to extraordinary journeys,where each miracle represents relentless pursuit.

25.name: Duel Cert
25.desc: A certificate earned in Trekker Duel. Can be exchanged for items in the Duel Shop.
25.literary: Bestowed by the Trekker Association, it's a testament to your prowess in Trekker Duel.Rumor has it that it can unlock hidden options in the Shop.

28.name: Urgent Hunt Order
28.desc: A certificate used for unlocking Proving Grounds.
28.literary: A hunting bounty posted by the Trekker Association.Be sure to gauge your strength before taking on the hunt.

29.name: Monolith Stairs Pass
29.desc: A pass used to initiate a Monolith Express.
29.literary: Once you have obtained the "Key to the Monolith Stairs," you can use the pass to go straight to the top and snag the ultimate "Record"... Yeah, like luck ever works that way.You still have to face every single twist and turn. This just saves you a bit of the boring slog.

30.name: Monolith Stairs Pass
30.desc: A pass used to initiate a Monolith Express.
30.literary: Once you have obtained the "Key to the Monolith Stairs," you can use the pass to go straight to the top and snag the ultimate "Record"... Yeah, like luck ever works that way.You still have to face every single twist and turn. This just saves you a bit of the boring slog.

31.name: Defender's Medal
31.desc: A medal obtained through Cataclysm Survivor. Can be exchanged for items in the Shop.
31.literary: A medal awarded to Trekkers who actively fight in the defense front.With enough badges, you can exchange them at the Association for generous rewards.—Perhaps this is the kind of currency that truly holds weight in a Trekker's circles.

34.name: Whispers of Decay
34.desc: A certificate obtained through A Finale Echoing. Can be exchanged for items in the Shop.
34.literary: A magic crystal bearing a low, lamenting hymn, overflowing with resentment and unease.

35.name: Acclaim of Ascension
35.desc: A certificate obtained through A Finale Echoing. Can be exchanged for items in the Shop.
35.literary: A magic crystal containing an intense, soaring melody, bearing joy and celebration.

36.name: Showdown Decree
36.desc: During the event, you get three challenge attempts per day.Each attempt gives you a 60-minute window to enter as many battles as you can.Simulation battles don't consume any Showdown Decree.After the challenge period ends, you can no longer use Showdown Decree to start new challenges, but any ongoing challenge can still be completed normally.

51.name: Starlight Core
51.desc: Used to activate research nodes in Monolith Research.
51.literary: Normally, the Monolith always appears pristine when you step in. So these cracks and flakes seem oddly out of place. Yet even these seemingly worthless bits of debris have become prized "research material" among scholars. And with that came fees and commissions.

61.name: Daily Tyrant Points
61.desc: Points obtained by completing daily quests. Reaching certain milestones will unlock daily rewards.

63.name: Weekly Tyrant Points
63.desc: Points obtained by completing Weekly Affairs. Reach milestones to unlock weekly rewards.

103.name: Amber
103.desc: Proof of invitation to add Amber to your squad
103.literary: Listen closely, and you might just catch the faint sound of a meowing cat.

107.name: Tilia
107.desc: Proof of invitation to add Tilia to your squad
107.literary: Pure and flawless, that's the heartfelt yearning of the "Guardian of Justice."

108.name: Kasimira
108.desc: Proof of invitation to add Kasimira to your squad
108.literary: The flames are still blazing, scorchingly hot.

110.name: Firenze
110.desc: Proof of invitation to add Firenze to your squad
110.literary: Perched atop the world's gaze, she surveys all beneath her, like a monarch overlooking her realm.In her tender grasp, her fingers trace the familiar, worn contours of an old chair.

111.name: Iris
111.desc: Proof of invitation to add Iris to your squad
111.literary: It's a serene dreamscape, a blissful day when all work is finished.

112.name: Noya
112.desc: Proof of invitation to add Noya to your squad
112.literary: It feels like standing atop a mountain peak, yet also adrift in the vastness of the ocean.A cooling breeze caresses my face, and before me lies an unending expanse of horizon.

113.name: Shimiao
113.desc: Proof of invitation to add Shimiao to your squad
113.literary: Beneath the cicada-filled tree in the afternoon academy, she finally relaxes in her dreams, shedding all her tensions.

116.name: Ridge
116.desc: Proof of invitation to add Ridge to your squad
116.literary: Driven by evasion and fear, she built a wall of despair in her heart.Yet, she subtly crafted tiny flaws, longing for someone to break through and reach her.

117.name: Jinglin
117.desc: Proof of invitation to add Jinglin to your squad
117.literary: It's another bustling business day with long lines of customers.Let's start by making that little goal a reality.

118.name: Coronis
118.desc: Proof of invitation to add Coronis to your squad
118.literary: The specimen room in the clinic is steadily filling up,but unfortunately, she still hasn't found the one that captures her heart the most.

119.name: Nanoha
119.desc: Proof of invitation to add Nanoha to your squad
119.literary: The room is filled with cakes that exude a rich milk aroma.The maid dances gracefully among the cups and plates, lost in her own world.

120.name: Canace
120.desc: Proof of invitation to add Canace to your squad
120.literary: Having cast aside their surnames, embraced their past, and charted their future,these heroes have long learned to brave the wind without a single complaint.

123.name: Ann
123.desc: Proof of invitation to add Ann to your squad
123.literary: Across the golden fields, two tiny figures are running.She is chasing the setting sun.

125.name: Freesia
125.desc: Proof of invitation to add Freesia to your squad
125.literary: Raindrops dance on her hair and splash at her feet.She strides forward through mud and blossoms, venturing bravely into the distance.

126.name: Flora
126.desc: Proof of invitation to add Flora to your squad
126.literary: Fueled by vengeance and ignited by passion,the blazing phoenix breaks free from its shackles, spreading its wings to soar into the vast wilderness and skies of freedom.

127.name: Teresa
127.desc: Proof of invitation to add Teresa to your squad
127.literary: On the day the maiden left, the earthy aroma after a light drizzle lingered vividly in her memory.She made a mark on the map, anticipating the wonderful surprises she would bring back upon her return.

132.name: Minova
132.desc: Proof of invitation to add Minova to your squad
132.literary: Strangers are the desks, the classroom, the uniform.Yet, your familiar smile is comforting.

133.name: Nazuka
133.desc: Proof of invitation to add Nazuka to your squad
133.literary: That young reformer always wants to carry the weight of the world on her shoulders alone.Never yielding, never settling.

134.name: Fuyuka
134.desc: Proof of invitation to add Fuyuka to your squad
134.literary: To protect her friends, she cradles the most invaluable treasure with utmost care.It bears the name of courage.

135.name: Mistique
135.desc: Proof of invitation to add Mistique to your squad
135.literary: Breaking News! Here comes the impartial, brave, fearless legendary witch again!Today's headline... Her Secrets!

141.name: Chixia
141.desc: Proof of invitation to add Chixia to your squad
141.literary: Give Chixia a brush and a bottle of ink—and let her bring her Xuanshi world to life.

142.name: Cosette
142.desc: Proof of invitation to add Cosette to your squad
142.literary: The past has sunk into the earth like fallen rain, feeding new sprouts that reach for the sun.From here on out, she will start a new life.

144.name: Chitose
144.desc: Proof of invitation to add Chitose to your squad
144.literary: The resolute flash of her blade spoke volumes.

147.name: Caramel
147.desc: Proof of invitation to add Caramel to your squad
147.literary: Spotlights and glowsticks paint a dreamscape. You, my shining star, please keep going.

149.name: Gerie
149.desc: Proof of invitation to add Gerie to your squad
149.literary: Between survival and annihilation, that grace alone must remain inviolable.

150.name: Laru
150.desc: Proof of invitation to add Laru to your squad
150.literary: Always working hard at half-assing it.Slacking off is a lifetime commitment.

155.name: Shia
155.desc: Proof of invitation to add Shia to your squad
155.literary: Piercing the sea mist and crashing through the waves, a familiar scent will guide you home.

156.name: Nazuna
156.desc: Proof of invitation to add Nazuna to your squad
156.literary: She only let her childish side show around those she trusts most.

158.name: Snowish Laru
158.desc: Proof of invitation to add Snowish Laru to your squad
158.literary: Guard the children's innocent wishes as a spirit.

401.name: Everbright Wishes
401.desc: Valid for 30 days. Log in daily to receive 90 Stellanite Dust.

502.name: Cerulean Ticket
502.desc: A certificate used for recruiting in Limited Trekker Banner.
502.literary: Set the direction, embrace an unforgettable encounter.

503.name: Sprout Ticket
503.desc: A certificate used for recruiting in Permanent Trekker Banner.
503.literary: Set the direction, embrace an unforgettable encounter.

510.name: Snowish Limited Ticket
510.desc: An exclusive certificate used for recruiting in Holy Night Gift Rush!
510.literary: Set the direction, embrace an unforgettable encounter.

511.name: Snowish Exclusive 10x Draw Ticket
511.desc: An exclusive certificate used for Recruit x10 in Holy Night Gift Rush!
511.literary: Set the direction, embrace an unforgettable encounter.

602.name: Gold Disc
602.desc: A certificate used for recruiting in Limited Disc Banner.
602.literary: Clean up the memory hall and look for the eternal symphony.

603.name: Silver Disc
603.desc: A certificate used for recruiting in Permanent Disc Banner.
603.literary: Clean up the memory hall and look for the eternal symphony.

1000.name: Radiant Soul Key
1000.literary: A soul key, radiant and brimming with emotional power.It unseals the latent talents buried in the deepest corners of the soul...

1001.name: Charming Soul Key
1001.literary: A soul key, radiant and brimming with emotional power.It ignites the talents hidden in the depths of a soul...

10303.name: Playful Innocence
10303.desc: Certificate that unlocks Amber's exclusive appearance "Playful Innocence"!
10303.literary: Woven from flowing flames and adorned with golden clouds—a majestic spirit, fierce and free.Rawr—

10703.name: This Is My Justice!
10703.desc: Certificate that unlocks Tilia's exclusive appearance "This Is My Justice!"!
10703.literary: Suit up, transform! My fighting spirit burns hotter than the sun!Clad in the armor of justice, I'll defend every street like a knight—This is my justice!

11103.name: The 1/365th of You
11103.desc: Certificate that unlocks Iris's exclusive appearance "The 1/365th of You"!
11103.literary: In the pale winter sunlight, you hold a warm drink as your breath creates a white mist. You, who see yourself as just ordinary, are the one who makes this day special.

11203.name: Lingering Sunlight
11203.desc: Certificate that unlocks Noya's exclusive appearance: Lingering Sunlight!
11203.literary: Sun, sand, and sea—time to slip into your swimsuit!Feel the warm sun on your skin and the gentle kiss of the waves. Summer's calling, just don't forget your sunscreen!

11903.name: When Distant Winds Rise
11903.desc: Certificate that unlocks Nanoha's exclusive appearance "When Distant Winds Rise"!
11903.literary: The wind sways the clouds as dust dances in sunlight. Only the flowers witness the moments we share.

12503.name: The Gift of Falling Snow
12503.desc: Certificate that unlocks Freesia's exclusive appearance "The Gift of Falling Snow"!
12503.literary: The Snowish Festival she dreams of is a warm, cozy fire, a glass of sweet wine in hand, her best friends' laughter, and a unique gift just for her—from you.

13203.name: Tipsy Daydream
13203.desc: Certificate that unlocks Minova's exclusive appearance "Tipsy Daydream"!
13203.literary: The coolness of the desk beneath my arms, the warmth of the sun on my back.The scent of books enchants me, as I drift into a gentle daydream.

13403.name: Probation Period Cleared!
13403.desc: Certificate that unlocks Fuyuka's exclusive appearance "Probation Period Cleared!"!
13403.literary: Clock in on time? Check. Prep the materials? Check. Work hard, stay focused... Whoa there, how did I mess it up again?

20003.name: Forest Elf Fang
20003.desc: Used for certain Trekker skill upgrade (Lv.7 to Lv.10).
20003.literary: A fang hunted from the beasts that haunt the forest.It's covered with eerie vines that seem to pulsate with a life of their own,whispering the protests of the forest.

20013.name: Crimson Tempter
20013.desc: Used for certain Trekker skill upgrade (Lv.7 to Lv.10).
20013.literary: Nestled deep in the forest, is it the flower...or the fruit of a mysterious parasitic plant?Countless blood-like mouths like these lure prey into their traps...

20023.name: Colossus Core
20023.desc: Used for certain Trekker skill upgrade (Lv.7 to Lv.10).
20023.literary: A core collected from the remnants of the Colossus.Indeed...it seems to know you; you are its chosen target.

20043.name: Wrath Beauty
20043.desc: Used for certain Trekker skill upgrade (Lv.7 to Lv.10).
20043.literary: The fully bloomed flower of "Lithe Beauty."It emits a strange, demoralizing scent of darkness and anxiety.

20053.name: Radiant Feather Crown
20053.desc: Used for certain Trekker skill upgrade (Lv.7 to Lv.10).
20053.literary: An accessory crafted from the tail feathers of the Emerald Blade.As a symbol of your triumph over the boss, wearing it may bring you more commission opportunities.

20063.name: Nightlit Haven
20063.desc: Used for certain Trekker skill upgrade (Lv.7 to Lv.10).
20063.literary: A hidden reef paradise atop the Hexhorn Whale's head.The sea giant's very body becomes a sanctuary where creatures live out their long lives in the winding maze, day after day, year after year.

20071.name: Backstage Ragged Hat
20071.desc: A basic material used for Trekker tier-up.
20071.literary: An old hat with torn fringes. It still carries dust that has risen from eerie dance moves.

20072.name: Spotlight Bowler
20072.desc: An intermediate material used for Trekker tier-up.
20072.literary: An elaborate bowler.In the spotlight, it is a reflection of the master's ever-shifting grace.

20073.name: Exeunt Bowler
20073.desc: An advanced material used for Trekker tier-up.
20073.literary: A top hat decorated with ornament.When the spotlight fades, its frenzy retreats like a receding tide.

20081.name: Count's Rewards
20081.desc: A basic material used for Trekker tier-up.
20081.literary: Mortal, this is the reward from great Count of the Duloos. You should show gratitude for his generosity.

20082.name: Count's Cellaring
20082.desc: An intermediate material used for Trekker tier-up.
20082.literary: I, the great Count of the Duloos, now grant you the treasure, a jar of vintage wine. Praise me for my generosity, mortal!

20083.name: Count's Gift
20083.desc: An advanced material used for Trekker tier-up.
20083.literary: Kneel down, mortal! Here is a gift from the great Count of the Duloos! Accept this supreme honor with gratitude and awe.

20091.name: Faint Wick
20091.desc: A basic material used for Trekker tier-up.
20091.literary: The unburned wick of Evernight Emberflies. It is so faint that it seems like it can never be ignited again.

20092.name: Lumen Essence
20092.desc: An intermediate material used for Trekker tier-up.
20092.literary: The essence of Evernight Emberflies. It was once brightly lit.

20093.name: Eternal Gloom Core
20093.desc: An advanced material used for Trekker tier-up.
20093.literary: The core of Evernight Emberflies. It refuses to close its eyes, and every crack is a sign of recurring frenzies.

20997.name: Random Boss Trekker Material
20997.desc: Grants a random basic material for Trekker tier-up.
20997.literary: A random basic material used for Trekker tier-up.

21003.name: Forest Elf Essence
21003.desc: Used for certain Trekker skill upgrade (Lv.7 to Lv.10).
21003.literary: In some parts, this mighty beast is known as the "Forest Lord." Legends say it's more than just a force of destruction: It's nature incarnate, a true king whose soul is bound to the forest it rules.

21013.name: Evil Bloom Essence
21013.desc: Used for certain Trekker skill upgrade (Lv.7 to Lv.10).
21013.literary: Cunning and spooky, it sets traps and shifts its form endlessly... Only the truly fearless can overcome its twisted evil and harness the power at its core.

21023.name: Colossus Essence
21023.desc: Used for certain Trekker skill upgrade (Lv.7 to Lv.10).
21023.literary: Its tall, imposing form was meant to stand in that mysterious and regal chamber.Whether it was the master's mistake to leave, or its own for following, no longer seems to matter with the passing of time.

21043.name: Wind Essence
21043.desc: Used for certain Trekker skill upgrade (Lv.7 to Lv.10).
21043.literary: It wasn't born of nature. Beneath its lovely facade runs poison, driven by the ruthless ambition of corporate schemers.

21053.name: Radiant Crown Essence
21053.desc: Used for certain Trekker skill upgrade (Lv.7 to Lv.10).
21053.literary: It was forced to dwell within this delicate cage, its wild nature howling and thrashing beneath the mask.

21063.name: Tidal Essence
21063.desc: Used for certain Trekker skill upgrade (Lv.7 to Lv.10).
21063.literary: A colossal shadow lurking beneath the deep sea. Each time it surfaces, it brings surging waves and the awe-inspiring force of nature.

21071.name: Eerie Breath
21071.desc: A basic material used for Discs tier-up.
21071.literary: Grasp the lingering aura on this eerie breath. You can still feel the force of the eerie power within, a call from another dimension.

21072.name: Phantom Step Remnant
21072.desc: An intermediate material used for Discs tier-up.
21072.literary: The lingering soul holds the purest essence of spirit. As you grasp it, the image of uncanny phantom step rises once more in your mind.

21073.name: Frenzied Waltz Essence
21073.desc: An advanced material used for Discs tier-up.
21073.literary: It enjoys the frenzied stage, bowing just in preparation for embracing more impassioned beats.

21081.name: Duloos Breath
21081.desc: A basic material used for Discs tier-up.
21081.literary: The great Count is unbeatable. It just fights to test the strength of the mortal and mercifully rewards them with treasure.

21082.name: Duloos Soul Remnant
21082.desc: An intermediate material used for Discs tier-up.
21082.literary: The great Count fights beyond the cause of victory. It just fools with reckless mortals to spend afternoon tea time and generously shares with them its cellaring.

21083.name: Duloos Essence
21083.desc: An advanced material used for Discs tier-up.
21083.literary: The great Count won't bear disgrace!The count pretends to be sleeping to let the mortal win, and the dropped fragment is its generous gift to the mortal for their perseverance.

21091.name: Faint Light Breath
21091.desc: A basic material used for Discs tier-up.
21091.literary: Grasp the lingering aura on this faint light. You can still feel its obsession with ever-glowing.

21092.name: Emberflies Soul
21092.desc: An intermediate material used for Discs tier-up.
21092.literary: The lingering soul holds the purest essence of spirit. As you grasp it, the image of touching glow rises once more in your mind. The stunning light is both a sword and a cage.

21093.name: Evernight Essence
21093.desc: An advanced material used for Discs tier-up.
21093.literary: It indulges in the night and shuns the day.It just hopes to have its own valuable time and freedom.

21997.name: Random Boss Disc Material
21997.desc: Grants a random basic material for Disc tier-up.

30001.name: Trekker's Guide
30001.desc: Grants a small amount of EXP for leveling up Trekkers.
30001.literary: A beginner's guide tailored for novice Trekkers.Even though it's just a few pages long, reading it will always be beneficial.

30002.name: Novice's Internship Journal
30002.desc: Grants a moderate amount of EXP for leveling up Trekkers.
30002.literary: A journal filled with handy tips for Trekkers.Read through a couple, and you'll avoid making mistakes your seniors made.

30003.name: Senior's Travel Journal
30003.desc: Grants a large amount of EXP for leveling up Trekkers.
30003.literary: Each page is packed with reflections and lessons learned.Its weight signifies not only the memories of the journey, but also the wisdom accumulated.

30004.name: Trekker's Handwritten Encyclopedia
30004.desc: Grants tons of EXP for leveling up Trekkers.
30004.literary: Absorbing knowledge without comprehension is futile; even the finest books deserve repeated perusals.A true Trekker has every line of their books etched in their memory.

32000.name: Chess Piece of Skill
32000.desc: A generic material used for Trekker skill upgrades.
32000.literary: For Trekkers, wisdom, skill and experience are more important than strength and magic.—One can always learn something by playing chess with the more experienced.

32001.name: Tapping Game Cartridge
32001.desc: A basic material used for Trekker skill upgrades.
32001.literary: Tap the buttons to the rhythm of the music—a game anyone can pick up. It's a fun and effortless way to improve one's coordination, making it a hit among Trekkers.

32002.name: Rhythm Game Cartridge
32002.desc: An intermediate material used for Trekker skill upgrades.
32002.literary: Step up your game with this challenging hardcore rhythm game. Most people struggle to keep up with so many notes.But, true virtuosos glide through with seamless elegance.

32003.name: Magic Sound Game Cartridge
32003.desc: An advanced material used for Trekker skill upgrades.
32003.literary: Enter the realm of "Boss's Tune," a music game series that pushes the limits. Only those with lightning-fast reflexes or perhaps an extra pair of hands dare to take up the challenge. Could this be the next step in human evolution?!

32011.name: Shooter Game Cartridge
32011.desc: A basic material used for Trekker skill upgrades.
32011.literary: Dodge bullets and blast your enemies to smithereens. This game features simple rules, but it significantly sharpens your reflexes.Trekkers often joke about these games, calling them "Little Butterflies."

32012.name: Barrage Game Cartridge
32012.desc: An intermediate material used for Trekker skill upgrades.
32012.literary: As the saying goes, "A little goes a long way," and "Barrage" is a testament to this. It evolves its gameplay purely through escalating difficulty. While ordinary players are still struggling for "survival," geniuses are already shooting for "high scores."

32013.name: Demon Bee Game Cartridge
32013.desc: An advanced material used for Trekker skill upgrades.
32013.literary: For all those previous shooter games, Trekkers would always boast, "It's nothing special..." But then "Demon Bee" showed up.Oh boy, is it a beast! Not a single soul has managed to clear the game without using continues or losing a life.Could this be the ultimate test of skill?

32021.name: Kung Fu Game Cartridge
32021.desc: A basic material used for Trekker skill upgrades.
32021.literary: Punch! Kick! Rising Dragon Strike! Knock your enemies off the stage!This Kung Fu game serves as both a battleground for Trekkers to hone their combat skills and a fantastic outlet for stress relief.

32022.name: Fighting Game Cartridge
32022.desc: An intermediate material used for Trekker skill upgrades.
32022.literary: To the masters, "fighting" is the "art of outflanking." In other words, patience often leads to victory—cultivating this hunter's mindset is crucial for protecting Trekkers.

32023.name: Phantom Game Cartridge
32023.desc: An advanced material used for Trekker skill upgrades.
32023.literary: Mindless attacks won't secure a win. Take the game "Phantom" as an example; there's an opponent who can seamlessly block 15 punches in the blink of an eye.If you can break through his defense, your combat skills will truly be unparalleled.

33001.name: Artifact Wishing Egg
33001.desc: Used to craft random common gifts in Material Crafting.
33001.literary: Each time a Monolith is explored, Wishing Eggs will appear along with Wishing Boxes and can be used to wish for common Artifacts.In addition to selling Artifacts to the people of the cities for money, Trekkers sometimes save some "leftovers" for themselves.

33011.name: Love Candle
33011.desc: A gift that increases a Trekker's Affinity by 150.
33011.literary: A marvelous Artifact that ignites with just a flick. It's a truly handy tool for Trekkers journeying through the Wilds.Strictly prohibited in dense forests!

33012.name: Blazing Wings
33012.desc: A gift that increases a Trekker's Affinity by 500.
33012.literary: Equipped with directional nozzles, this Artifact boasts enhanced capacity and firepower, making it perfect for heating food.Even in the Wilds, you can whip up delicious grilled meat patties that taste just like mom's!

33013.name: Fiery Honeypot
33013.desc: A gift that increases a Trekker's Affinity by 2,000.
33013.literary: With super-charged firepower and capacity, it can even serve as a weapon to fend off wild beasts.Be warned, it's banned from all forms of transportation in Nova's cities due to its hazardous nature. Yet, it remains a highly sought-after treasure among Trekkers, chefs, and acrobats!

33021.name: Card Photo Capturer
33021.desc: A gift that increases a Trekker's Affinity by 150.
33021.literary: The unveiling of camera Artifact marks another groundbreaking moment in the arts and media landscape.Some believe capturing a photo steals a part of one's soul, making it a niche hobby.

33022.name: Reflective Photo Capturer
33022.desc: A gift that increases a Trekker's Affinity by 500.
33022.literary: When the Reflective Photo Capturer first emerged, painters cried foul, fearing job loss. But soon, some embraced the change, adopting the title of "Photographist" and carving out a new field.

33023.name: Ultra-Precision Photo Capturer
33023.desc: A gift that increases a Trekker's Affinity by 2,000.
33023.literary: The ultimate dream Artifact for Photographists.With this, you can capture any fleeting moment from afar, preserving it forever on film...Still, maybe it's this fleeting nature that gives life its meaning.

33031.name: Portable Blower
33031.desc: A gift that increases a Trekker's Affinity by 150.
33031.literary: One of the most popular daily Artifacts in the Shop, and a must-have for many female Trekkers.Before this handy device, Novians would rely on magical spells or simply sitting in warm places to dry their wet hair.

33032.name: Exquisite Blower
33032.desc: A gift that increases a Trekker's Affinity by 500.
33032.literary: An upgraded hair dryer with precise temperature and speed settings, minimizing hair damage.Just like savoring a glass of fine red wine after a gourmet meal, using this after a refreshing bath takes your relaxation to the next level.

33033.name: Deluxe Blower
33033.desc: A gift that increases a Trekker's Affinity by 2,000.
33033.literary: An extremely expensive daily Artifact, exclusive to the boudoirs of aristocrats and legendary stars.Though boasting powerful functions, the owners often prefer to flaunt it as a status symbol rather than putting it to actual use.

33041.name: Whisper Wind Spinner
33041.desc: A gift that increases a Trekker's Affinity by 150.
33041.literary: A simple blowing device, compact and easy to carry, but don't expect too much when it comes to its cooling effect.

33042.name: Chilling Wind Spinner
33042.desc: A gift that increases a Trekker's Affinity by 500.
33042.literary: A cooling artifact that really makes a splash, but its size and weight make it less portable.However, it's a potent weapon against the heat and irritability.

33043.name: Blazing Wind Spinner
33043.desc: A gift that increases a Trekker's Affinity by 2,000.
33043.literary: An Artifact that is hailed as the ultimate savior against scorching heat,It not only rescues any Novian from the deadly grip of blazing summers but also boasts a pivoting function, spreading its benevolent coolness far and wide.

33051.name: Rising Star
33051.desc: A gift that increases a Trekker's Affinity by 150.
33051.literary: Push the button, and it'll radiate a warm, inspiring burst of colored light. Perfect for live performances to ignite the atmosphere!You're my top pick!

33052.name: Emerging Talent
33052.desc: A gift that increases a Trekker's Affinity by 500.
33052.literary: Even though not a superstar yet, this raw gem already shines so brightly... Is this what it feels like to grow together?—You over there, and you over here—I see you all!

33053.name: Shining Star
33053.desc: A gift that increases a Trekker's Affinity by 2,000.
33053.literary: Even if you've become a megastar, I'll be in the stands, waving the glow stick for you with all my heart once more!In the instant our eyes meet, that's when magic happens.

33061.name: Stellanite Enchantment
33061.desc: A gift that increases a Trekker's Affinity by 150.
33061.literary: It's said that placing it beside your bed will summon stars to your dreams.Did these twinkles traverse the night sky just for us?

33062.name: Moonlit Companion
33062.desc: A gift that increases a Trekker's Affinity by 500.
33062.literary: Display a moon at home to keep you company.This mysterious ruler of the night, whose secrets have remained hidden for millennia,Is both the mirror of the day and a reflection of our souls.

33063.name: Cosmic Form
33063.desc: A gift that increases a Trekker's Affinity by 2,000.
33063.literary: Scholars have yet to fathom the universe,So the Starry Tyrant grants wisdom from beyond this world,Crystallizing truth into tangible shapes.

33071.name: Summer Chill Crushed Ice
33071.desc: A gift that increases a Trekker's Affinity by 150.
33071.literary: Escape the scorching heat of summer with a delightful bowl of refreshing crushed ice!

33072.name: Fragrant Ice Delight
33072.desc: A gift that increases a Trekker's Affinity by 500.
33072.literary: Wandering the streets on a lazy afternoon, I passed by an ice cream shop with inviting chill, dreaming of sharing a sweet treat with you on my next visit.

33073.name: Sweet IceFurry
33073.desc: A gift that increases a Trekker's Affinity by 2,000.
33073.literary: I've finally asked you out. The "Buy One, Get One Half Off" deal was just my excuse.My favorite flavor? Same as yours!

33081.name: Gilded Ceramic Bowl
33081.desc: A gift that increases a Trekker's Affinity by 150.
33081.literary: This uniquely shaped tea bowl is said to attract purring mystical beasts when placed at your doorstep. The more delicious the food inside, the more cracks will appear on its surface—greedy beasts often knock it over in their haste.

33082.name: Blossom Porcelain Cup
33082.desc: A gift that increases a Trekker's Affinity by 500.
33082.literary: A treasured heirloom passed down through generations, delicately crafted with intricate designs of azure blossoms on its pristine white glaze. Whenever esteemed guests visit, the enthusiastic Loong retrieves it from the wooden cabinet to brew a cup of warm tea.

33083.name: Mystic Potion Kettle
33083.desc: A gift that increases a Trekker's Affinity by 2,000.
33083.literary: This kettle pulses with enigmatic energy. It looks like It's made of glass, but It's actually crafted from a special material, making it robust enough to withstand any harsh environment. Whether it holds a life-saving antidote or a mesmerizing poison is entirely up to the whim of its maker.

33901.name: Common Choice Box
33901.desc: Grants a common gift of your choice.
33901.literary: Wanna give a little surprise to your closest companion? Pick one from these lightweight and practical artifacts—they're perfect gifts for Trekkers!

33902.name: Exquisite Choice Box
33902.desc: Grants an exquisite gift of your choice.
33902.literary: How to express your heartfelt gratitude and blessings? Pick an elegant and exquisite artifact here as a symbol of your unspoken bond!

33903.name: Deluxe Choice Box
33903.desc: Grants a deluxe gift of your choice.
33903.literary: What kind of gift can truly last forever and be cherished for generations? Pick a luxurious gift that captures your heart, and let it serve as the perfect testament to your friendship...or deeper sentiments!

50001.literary: A common recyclable item.A practical option for repairing Runic Discs.

50003.name: Elegant Rim
50003.desc: Grants a large amount of EXP for upgrading Discs.
50003.literary: A Runic Disc adorned with exquisite rimming.Only a captivating melody can match its sophisticated elegance.

50004.name: Starlit Colored Glass
50004.desc: Grants tons of EXP for upgrading Discs.
50004.literary: A Runic Disc crafted from glass, radiating the luminous glow of the starry sky.The essence of ritual, after all, is a form of enchanting magic.

73104.desc: Currency earned via active participation in [Radiant Messenger, Holy Night Spirit]. Can be used to redeem items in the Event Shop.

73201.literary: A banner sent by the Trekker Association to recognize Trekkers who have fully explored the Monolith and contributed Records—"All for one, one for all."

211001.name: Crisp Morning
211001.literary:
Standing in the wilderness, a gentle breeze caresses.
Another day blooms anew.

211002.name: Sunny Breeze
211002.literary:
A golden sea, brimming with the joy of harvest.
Make sure to eat well and take care of yourself!

211003.name: Indigo Sunset
211003.literary:
A tiny broom soaring with grand dreams.
The cloud-hidden scenery awaits tomorrow's discovery.

211004.name: Pink Dream
211004.literary:
A princess revered by all, a hero returning with honors.
Dreams are blind to status; your harvest grows with every step you take.

211005.name: Lonely Dunes
211005.literary:
The sand sea engulfs the horizon, obscuring the journey's end.
It's time to pause and catch your breath.

211006.name: Sweet Creek
211006.literary:
A sparkling spring kisses your skirt hem, stopping you in your tracks.
Quench your thirst first, then brace yourself for the thorny path ahead.

211007.name: Starlit Hope
211007.literary:
Shimmering stars light up the night sky.
Brave maidens, it's time to embark on your journey!

211008.name: Homeward Path
211008.literary:
Gentle starlight, farewell to today.
The bell rings to close today's business!

212001.name: Grand Feast
212001.literary:
I can't wait!
I'm desperate to savor my favorite iced black tea, sweetened with sugar, topped with creamy foam, infused with tangerine slices, sprinkled with chocolate crumbs, and blended with pineapple and mango juice!

212002.name: Whoopla
212002.literary:
Spinning around in circles, vying for the chairs.
Only those who grab a chair get to sit down.
Wait, aren't we playing "Freeze Dance"?

212003.name: Elysium
212003.literary:
To Whom It May Concern,
With admiration for your outstanding dance skills,
you are warmly invited to this never-ending dance party.

212005.name: Flare Frenzy
212005.literary:
Pump up the jam, and keep the dance floor thumpin'!
Let the volume shatter the skies, let our passion ignite the clouds!
My adrenaline has skyrocketed to its absolute limit!

212006.name: Auspicious Glow
212006.literary:
At the dawn of creation,
shattered beliefs hovered above the horizon, casting its glow over the world.
Humans leaped over mountains, gazing boldly at the gods.
And then, heaven and earth split, the light dimmed, and days merged into an endless flow.

212007.name: Brave the Wind
212007.literary:
The wind awakens all creatures and paints the forest with a splash of vibrant colors, whispering the news of the party to every corner of the woods and caves:
The grand celebration of the forest and its elves is about to begin!

212008.name: Bubbles
212008.literary:
Keep the joyful moments for yourself.
Embrace it as a break—immerse yourself in this refreshing, fleeting joy.

212009.name: Eclipse
212009.literary:
Its grudge still rages within, burning fiercely.
"——! ——————!!"
Alas, it's hard to comprehend its sorrowful cries.

212010.name: Fortitude
212010.literary:
Once the war horn sounds, there's no going back.
Fight! Fight until the bitter end!

213003.name: Scorching Night's End
213003.literary:
On the stage enveloped by cheers, they shine brightly as they play their final melody.
The tumultuous emotions ignite the notes, consuming this night with fiery passion.

213004.name: Twin Moon Mischief

213005.name: ★Bam Bam Girl★
213005.literary:
Bammm! The cells are splitting!
Gurgleee! The brains are boiling!
Sliced right from the top,
one me multiplies into a thousand—how do you find the true me?

213006.name: Good Night
213006.literary:
Sinking into the cozy embrace of my soft bed, I find myself utterly unwilling to stir.
If we drift off together, will our dreams intertwine?

213007.name: Emerald Dream
213007.literary:
Golden birds flap their wings, splitting the dreamscape as soft as clouds.
In the cracks where memories weave, we will eventually meet the ones we long to see.

213008.name: Tranquil Retreat
213008.literary: The scenery along the journey is a gift we should appreciate. Let's take it slow, bring some snacks, and enjoy this bright, sunny break—it'll surely add a joyful chapter to our memories.

213009.name: Rainy Tune
213009.literary: Warm raindrops trickle down from head to toe, sliding down every inch of my skin. Ah—choo! It's not a cold, just the soap bubbles tickling me again.

213010.name: Steam Syndrome
213010.literary:
The whirling harbor breeze,
The hot air from the steaming baskets...
As you lean in close, your breath merges with.
The neon-hued vapors, blurring my vision.

213011.name: Meow Rhythm
213011.literary: Beyond the veil of silence and solemnity, is there another side of you that I haven't yet discovered? Electronic-distorted notes peel away the mundane facade, revealing a tender gaze under the neon glow that beckons me toward you.

213012.name: Starry Night Ode
213012.literary:
With the earth as our stage and the starry sky as our backdrop,
Listen up, universe—this is our moment to shine!

213013.name: Leaf Her to Me
213013.literary:
Dart through fields of wheat and play in maple forests, pausing where the seasons meet.
Oh, sun-kissed child, hide away, before the pains of growing up can find you.

213014.name: The Knight's Smith
213014.literary:
Tighten the screws, apply the grease.
Behind every great knight is an even greater blacksmith.
Safe travels—and don't ride too fast!

213015.name: Unknown Fragrance
213015.literary:
I smile often, yet true happiness is a rare guest.
For that scent, once vibrant, now fades and drifts further away.
Yet, whenever I reach for it, there's a stinging pain in my heart...

213016.name: Cage of Roses
213016.literary:
You've tasted the sweet forbidden fruit,
now you're the goddess of art.
Stand as the sole, ever-blooming rose in this pond of love and desire.
Sing, dance, shine, and repeat.
Keep going till the strings break, never stop.

213017.name: ★Rolling Life★
213017.literary:
Summer wraps up in a blur of sweat, yet there's still time to touch up for the next show.
In the corner of a winter celebration, I score the last ice cream cone before closing.
No matter how life is divided between work and leisure,
I'm still me, whole and unchanged.

213018.name: Soda Shopping
213018.literary:
On this eagerly anticipated day,
Standing before the dazzling shelves,
Which beverage holds the most anticipated flavor?
If you're torn between decisions,
Then take them all with you!

213019.name: Delusion
213019.literary:
Shimmering like fragile bubbles, they are dreams woven from pure imagination.
As these dreams burst and their shimmer fades, they uncover the purest truth,
whispering it all in silence.

213020.name: The Shining
213020.literary:
The moment wood splinters flew, a ravenous hunger burst through the door.
"No—get away from my emergency food stash! Aaaaah!"

213021.name: Miraculous Anthem
213021.literary:
Mirrors never tell lies;
they beckon you in and bid you farewell.
Your fate is inscribed on a particle of drifting dust,
while divine prophecy mirrors itself in my gaze.

213022.name: Love River's Curse
213022.literary:
Here lies the gateway to the Inferno.
It leads straight to the abyss of sin.
I wait by the riverbank, illuminating your sorrowful journey ahead,
blessing you to plunge into my eternal love.

213023.name: Pure White
213023.literary:
You skillfully push open the door,
And her pristine wings bring solace to your aching heart.
Together, you share a serene silence, a peaceful bond just between the two of you.
You know that her silence is her ultimate compassion towards you.
And your visit is the sole redemption she can ever hope for.

213024.name: Holiday Bubble
213024.literary:
"Hey, regular! Good to see ya! Your usual?"
"Huh? This seat's for toddlers only?"
"Eh, rules are made to be broken, right? Nobody's watching anyway!"
"Zoning out is adult paradise!"

Perfect vacation goals right here!
Resting on the register, she savors a dream, tart and sweet.

213025.name: Sweet Invitation
213025.literary:
O little bunny,
close your eyes and drift to sleep,
I'll cradle you in the arms of the night;

O little bunny,
rest your head and dream sweetly,
I promise you the sweetest treat of all.

213026.name: Vent It Out ♥
213026.literary:
"La-la-la—welcome home, Master! ♥"
"Whether it's the weariness in your heart or the misfortune at your side,"
"I will personally help you sweep all that nasty trash away!"
"Let me turn my energy into your magic! ♥"
"Heaven's cutest maid, Beatrixa, at your service! ♥"

With a clear, lively voice and an impossibly cute demeanor,
she gave her all every day
to deliver healing and hope to her fans across the Nova Continent.

214001.name: Meowing Cat God
214001.literary:
Humans are born alone.
Only in the heat of battle do we truly feel alive.
Huh? Cool guys don't look at explosions? Fine, I heard you—

214002.name: Sky, Flowers, Poem
214002.literary:
Like flower petals, your departing form dissolves,
Beneath starlit nights, our vows still warm my palm,
These perfumed days bring thoughts of you, despite my own will.

214004.name: Wisteria Dream
214004.literary:
Look who's here—two little soft kittens on my knee?
Afternoon tea time stretches far.
Sleep soundly. Let purple wisteria shade your beautiful dreams.

214005.name: Sunlit Blossom
214005.literary:
The blossoms drift in rainy haze,
That flowered in bright sunny days.
A rainbow's gleam within my hand—
Could such beauty ever stay?

214006.name: Witch's Swing
214006.literary:
The witch stands proud, head held high,
Granting honey, venom, and love divine.
You who failed to choose your princess right,
Embrace this cruel pleasure, and dance with me tonight?

214007.name: Midnight Mayhem
214007.literary:
They set the rules of right and wrong,
but if you loathe these bindings, rise as a midnight knight.
Even if bloodied and broken, we're staying true to who we are!
To those arrogant jerks:
"See this mighty fist?"
"After the clock strikes twelve, this is our domain!"

214009.name: New Star Prelude
214009.literary:
Only one day of food left. Our wallets are empty. The Oasis's Grace is running low...
We've staked everything on this Monolith commission...
—Still, when it's time for the group photo, don't forget to smile!

214010.name: Prayer Beneath Light
214010.literary:
We beseech Thee, have mercy; heed our plea.
Goddess, do the cries of mortals reach Thine ears?
...
—Each word finds Me, finds Us all.
We shall guide humanity towards its glorious destiny.

214011.name: Summer Afternoon Rain
214011.literary:
Before looking back at the start, what seemed the end was just
the start of a new chapter.
Are you happy as you've always dreamed you'd be?
Let's meet again tomorrow.

214012.name: Those with Ambition
214012.literary:
On United Harvest's grand design, Philae stands as just a single point.
From here, I shall draw a perfect circle, claiming the entire Nova.
—Follow me. Pledge loyalty. March ever onward.

214013.name: Voyage Blueprint
214013.literary:
"First, we need a ship, then courage, and lastly, faith."
The adventurer pinned the map
While whitecaps rage from point to point
Wild waters crash and beckon towards mysteries
She waits for kindred souls to sail.

214014.name: Sweet Times
214014.literary: We trekked, picked, and laughed with our friends, sharing sweet fruit that burst with juice in our mouths.

214015.name: Deer's Song
214015.literary:
Deer call softly in the grove, wild grass their sweet feast.
A maiden rests in afternoon shade, where sunbeams dance and weave.
Like wind through time the moments flow, "Click"—a memory to keep.

214017.name: Fireworks
214017.literary:
Like a human life, fireworks bloom, flourish, and fade—
brief yet brilliant, leaving their unique mark across the night sky.
It's much like a Trekker's endless quest to climb the Monolith,
all for that one day when they might finally hold the stars in their hands...

214018.name: Lemon & Black Tea
214018.literary:
With guilt my heart was heavy worn, to heal the bridge that had been torn.
Thought friendship's door was closed for good,
Till here we sit, just as we should.
New décor graces these old walls, new packages the sweet food calls.
One drink runs hot, one drink runs cold,
Same taste remains from days of old.

214019.name: One Shot, One Down
214019.literary:
Kasimira, are you ready?
This is round 37 and our final match for today.

Too bad, just one shot shy.
If that shot had landed, you'd have had me beat.
Chaton, your hand wavered at the critical moment.

Just the thought of besting you gets my adrenaline pumping!
Let's do it again!

Rack the gun, we've got the next commission to prep for.

—Looks like Chaton's challenge isn't over yet.

214020.name: Sparkling Moment
214020.literary:
"Uneventful days aren't worth recording."
"Dull little things aren't worth recording."
"Repetitive work isn't worth recording."
But...are they truly worthless?
A teammate's reminder before you head out, the wrong turn you took, the smiles and thanks you received...
These ordinary fragments of memory condense into tiny points of light.
Even if the paper turns yellow with time, the brilliance of each day will never be forgotten.

214021.name: United by Fate
214021.literary:
Friends, companions...whatever the name, they all embody the same group of souls united by fate. They converge when the threads of fate intertwine, and disperse when they unwind.
What we can do is cherish every fleeting moment of this reunion, laughing and playing with all our hearts, and etching those precious memories deep into our hearts.
And as the hour of parting draws near, we cling to the hope of a future encounter, anticipating the day we shall meet again.

214022.name: The Meow
214022.literary:
Behold, something looms in the dark.
Listen closely, do you hear those footsteps echoing?
Odd, a sudden shiver runs down my spine.

A faulty projector, an unknown film reel, and eerie visuals flickering...
A Trekker's camp at midnight, an uninvited guest, and an unexpected visitor.
"Meow—"
The silence envelops all. You close the door, but it has already slipped inside.

214023.name: Colors Pierce the Grey
214023.literary:
We had to take a day off now and then.
Escape the gang fights and the daily grind,
step out under a clear sky, and spray paint a rainbow of our own across it.

214024.name: One, Two, Three, Jump!
214024.literary:
A rope
dangled from a sunlit ledge,
dropping into the long-forgotten ruins.
The girl grabbed it
and rappelled down.
"Hah, just some treasure?
Watch me haul it up!"

214026.name: Sword Against Stream
214026.literary:
Damp hair clung to her back.
Her clothes were a mess, yet the air was stiflingly still.
Carrying a heavy heart, even the falling petals seemed to weigh her down.
As the rain fell endlessly, your silhouette began to blur.

214027.name: Mystic Brushstrokes
214027.literary:
Brush and ink are her weapons.
On the stretched rice paper,
She weaves her magic, each brushstroke dancing in unconventional places.
This is her realm, a world of enchantment solely under her command.

214028.name: Daylight Garden
214028.literary:
A petal without a name or number
drifts into the silent garden,
carrying a blush of crimson and a vision of pure white,
settling into a golden specimen, alongside a vanished dream.

214030.name: A Moment in the Afternoon
214030.literary:
The girl burst in with the afternoon sun,
bringing with her the aroma of snacks.
Fries? Grilled fish? Or a loaf of fluffy, warm bread?
You had to grab something
to enjoy this stolen moment of peace.

214031.name: The Clash of Blade and Axe
214031.literary:
An alarm blared as blade met axe.
The cage shattered, and she plunged into the abyss.
Through the crimson rain, she met your eyes.

214032.name: Dream Factory of ☆Truth
214032.literary:
Facts captured.
Photos printed.
Story broadcast.
Welcome to the witches' Dream Factory of ☆Truth!

214033.name: Dancing with the Bones
214033.literary:
Ah, welcome to my ball, my dear patient.
Listen, the music is playing. Come, dance with my collection among these phantom bubbles.

214036.name: The Lost Pilgrim
214036.literary:
Body bound, soul eroded,
even pain masquerades as a mire of salvation.
The fallen priestess still wanders
on a pilgrimage with no answers and no end,
awaiting a righteous one to grant her release.

214037.name: Claw the Claw
214037.literary:
The children of the Ash District tell a legend:
when despair grips the world and tears loved ones apart,
a green-haired heroine called the "Lord of the Prize Claw" and her brave companions
will lead everyone to catch the last glimmer of hope and reunite with their families.

214038.name: Ripples of Nostalgia
214038.literary:
Floating on a thousand crests,
a translucent, shimmering thing.
Escaping the searing summer heat,
drifting along with the migrating fish.

214039.name: Summer Sanctuary
214039.literary:
I long for the sea breeze to linger, for the waves to remain.
I pray for the sunset to stretch endlessly, for the starlight to never fade.
I wish to share with you alone—a summer that belongs to us.

214040.name: Fist of Courage
214040.literary:
To protect your companions, to summon the courage and become your best self,
strike your fist at the colossal enemy,
and clear the path to a future full of hope.

214041.name: A Gift for the Journey
214041.literary:
A sleigh full of gifts
guided by the messenger
heading toward the sunrise and its destination
except—
shouldn't reindeer be pulling it?!

214043.name: The Bud of Change
214043.literary:
Beneath the soil steeped in conspiracy and intrigue,
Watchful, calculating gazes interweave.
Something is struggling to break through the earth.

214048.name: Snowy Night Surprise
214048.literary:
The winter wind carries prayers from afar
The messenger arrives with blessings and gifts
Stepping into view as the midnight bells ring
This Snowish Festival gift is for you, who never lost your childish wonder

221001.name: Crisp Morning Melody
221001.desc: Material required for the Crescendo of specific Discs.
221001.literary: Standing in the wilderness, a gentle breeze caresses.Another day blooms anew.

221002.name: Sunny Breeze Melody
221002.desc: Material required for the Crescendo of specific Discs.
221002.literary: A golden sea, brimming with the joy of harvest.Make sure to eat well and take care of yourself!

221003.name: Evening Melody
221003.desc: Material required for the Crescendo of specific Discs.
221003.literary: A tiny broom soaring with grand dreams.The cloud-hidden scenery awaits tomorrow's discovery.

221004.name: Pink Dream Melody
221004.desc: Material required for the Crescendo of specific Discs.
221004.literary: A princess revered by all, a hero returning with honors.Dreams are blind to status; your harvest grows with every step you take.

221005.name: Lonely Dunes Melody
221005.desc: Material required for the Crescendo of specific Discs.
221005.literary: The sand sea engulfs the horizon, obscuring the journey's end.It's time to pause and catch your breath.

221006.name: Sweet Creek Melody
221006.desc: Material required for the Crescendo of specific Discs.
221006.literary: A sparkling spring kisses your skirt hem, stopping you in your tracks.Quench your thirst first, then brace yourself for the thorny path ahead.

221007.name: Starlit Hope Melody
221007.desc: Material required for the Crescendo of specific Discs.
221007.literary: Shimmering stars light up the night sky.Brave maidens, it's time to embark on your journey!

221008.name: Homeward Path Melody
221008.desc: Material required for the Crescendo of specific Discs.
221008.literary: Gentle starlight, farewell to today.The bell rings to close today's business!

222001.name: Grand Feast Melody
222001.desc: Material required for the Crescendo of specific Discs.
222001.literary: I can't wait!I'm desperate to savor my favorite iced black tea, sweetened with sugar, topped with creamy foam, infused with tangerine slices, sprinkled with chocolate crumbs, and blended with pineapple and mango juice!

222002.name: Whoopla Melody
222002.desc: Material required for the Crescendo of specific Discs.
222002.literary: Spinning around in circles, vying for the chairs.Only those who grab a chair get to sit down.Wait, aren't we playing "Freeze Dance"?

222003.name: Elysium Melody
222003.desc: Material required for the Crescendo of specific Discs.
222003.literary: To Whom It May Concern,With admiration for your outstanding dance skills,you are warmly invited to this never-ending dance party.

222005.name: Flare Frenzy Melody
222005.desc: Material required for the Crescendo of specific Discs.
222005.literary: Pump up the jam, and keep the dance floor thumpin'!Let the volume shatter the skies, let our passion ignite the clouds!My adrenaline has skyrocketed to its absolute limit!

222006.name: Auspicious Glow Melody
222006.desc: Material required for the Crescendo of specific Discs.
222006.literary: At the dawn of creation,shattered beliefs hovered above the horizon, casting its glow over the world.Humans leaped over mountains, gazing boldly at the gods.And then, heaven and earth split, the light dimmed, and days merged into an endless flow.

222007.name: Brave the Wind Melody
222007.desc: Material required for the Crescendo of specific Discs.
222007.literary: The wind awakens all creatures and paints the forest with a splash of vibrant colors, whispering the news of the party to every corner of the woods and caves:The grand celebration of the forest and its elves is about to begin!

222008.name: Bubbles Melody
222008.desc: Material required for the Crescendo of specific Discs.
222008.literary: Keep the joyful moments for yourself.Embrace it as a break—immerse yourself in this refreshing, fleeting joy.

222009.name: Eclipse Melody
222009.desc: Material required for the Crescendo of specific Discs.
222009.literary: Its grudge still rages within, burning fiercely."——! ——————!!"Alas, it's hard to comprehend its sorrowful cries.

222010.name: Fortitude Melody
222010.desc: Material required for the Crescendo of specific Discs.
222010.literary: Once the war horn sounds, there's no going back.Fight! Fight until the bitter end!

223003.name: Scorching Night's End Melody
223003.desc: Material required for the Crescendo of specific Discs.
223003.literary: On the stage enveloped by cheers, they shine brightly as they play their final melody.The tumultuous emotions ignite the notes, consuming this night with fiery passion.

223004.name: Twin Moon Mischief Melody
223004.desc: Material required for the Crescendo of specific Discs.
223004.literary: The charming and elegant Ashwind Twin Moons;the wise and witty protagonist.Black holes loom, foreshadowing a dark tomorrow for you all!

223005.name: ★Bam Bam Girl★ Melody
223005.desc: Material required for the Crescendo of specific Discs.
223005.literary: Bammm! The cells are splitting!Gurgleee! The brains are boiling!Sliced right from the top,one me multiplies into a thousand—how do you find the true me?

223006.name: Good Night Melody
223006.desc: Material required for the Crescendo of specific Discs.
223006.literary: Sinking into the cozy embrace of my soft bed, I find myself utterly unwilling to stir.If we drift off together, will our dreams intertwine?

223007.name: Emerald Glade Melody
223007.desc: Material required for the Crescendo of specific Discs.
223007.literary: Golden birds flap their wings, splitting the dreamscape as soft as clouds.In the cracks where memories weave, we will eventually meet the ones we long to see.

223008.name: Tranquil Retreat Melody
223008.desc: Material required for the Crescendo of specific Discs.
223008.literary: The scenery along the journey is a gift we should appreciate. Let's take it slow, bring some snacks, and enjoy this bright, sunny break—it'll surely add a joyful chapter to our memories.

223009.name: Rainy Tune Melody
223009.desc: Material required for the Crescendo of specific Discs.
223009.literary: Warm raindrops trickle down from head to toe, sliding down every inch of my skin. Ah—choo! It's not a cold, just the soap bubbles tickling me again.

223010.name: Steam Syndrome Melody
223010.desc: Material required for the Crescendo of specific Discs.
223010.literary: The whirling harbor breeze,The hot air from the steaming baskets...As you lean in close, your breath merges with.The neon-hued vapors, blurring my vision.

223011.name: Meow Rhythm Melody
223011.desc: Material required for the Crescendo of specific Discs.
223011.literary: Beyond the veil of silence and solemnity, is there another side of you that I haven't yet discovered? Electronic-distorted notes peel away the mundane facade, revealing a tender gaze under the neon glow that beckons me toward you.

223012.name: Starry Night Ode Melody
223012.desc: Material required for the Crescendo of specific Discs.
223012.literary: With the earth as our stage and the starry sky as our backdrop,Listen up, universe—this is our moment to shine!

223013.name: Leaf Her to Me Melody
223013.desc: Material required for the Crescendo of specific Discs.
223013.literary: Dart through fields of wheat and play in maple forests, pausing where the seasons meet.Oh, sun-kissed child, hide away, before the pains of growing up can find you.

223014.name: The Knight's Smith Melody
223014.desc: Material required for the Crescendo of specific Discs.
223014.literary: Tighten the screws, apply the grease.Behind every great knight is an even greater blacksmith.Safe travels—and don't ride too fast!

223015.name: Unknown Fragrance Melody
223015.desc: Material required for the Crescendo of specific Discs.
223015.literary: I smile often, yet true happiness is a rare guest.For that scent, once vibrant, now fades and drifts further away.Yet, whenever I reach for it, there's a stinging pain in my heart...

223016.name: Cage of Roses Melody
223016.desc: Material required for the Crescendo of specific Discs.
223016.literary: You've tasted the sweet forbidden fruit,now you're the goddess of art.Stand as the sole, ever-blooming rose in this pond of love and desire.Sing, dance, shine, and repeat.Keep going till the strings break, never stop.

223017.name: ★Rolling Life★ Melody
223017.desc: Material required for the Crescendo of specific Discs.
223017.literary: Summer wraps up in a blur of sweat, yet there's still time to touch up for the next show.In the corner of a winter celebration, I score the last ice cream cone before closing.No matter how life is divided between work and leisure,I'm still me, whole and unchanged.

223018.name: Soda Shopping Melody
223018.desc: Material required for the Crescendo of specific Discs.
223018.literary: On this eagerly anticipated day,Standing before the dazzling shelves,Which beverage holds the most exciting flavor?If you can't decide,Why not just take them all~

223019.name: Delusion Melody
223019.desc: Material required for the Crescendo of specific Discs.
223019.literary: Shimmering like fragile bubbles, they are dreams woven from pure imagination.As these dreams burst and their shimmer fades, they uncover the purest truth,whispering it all in silence.

223020.name: The Shining Melody
223020.desc: Material required for the Crescendo of specific Discs.
223020.literary: The moment wood splinters flew, a ravenous hunger burst through the door."No—get away from my emergency food stash! Aaaaah!"

223021.name: Miraculous Anthem Melody
223021.desc: Material required for the Crescendo of specific Discs.
223021.literary: Mirrors never tell lies;they beckon you in and bid you farewell.Your fate is inscribed on a particle of drifting dust,while divine prophecy mirrors itself in my gaze.

223022.name: Love Curse Melody
223022.desc: Material required for the Crescendo of specific Discs.
223022.literary: Here lies the gateway to the Inferno.It leads straight to the abyss of sin.I wait by the riverbank, illuminating your sorrowful journey ahead,blessing you to plunge into my eternal love.

223023.name: Pure White Melody
223023.desc: Material required for the Crescendo of specific Discs.
223023.literary: You skillfully push open the door,And her pristine wings bring solace to your aching heart.Together, you share a serene silence, a peaceful bond just between the two of you.You know that her silence is her ultimate compassion towards you.And your visit is the sole redemption she can ever hope for.

223024.name: Holiday Bubble Melody
223024.desc: Material required for the Crescendo of specific Discs.
223024.literary: "Hey, regular! Good to see ya! Your usual?""Huh? This seat's for toddlers only?""Eh, rules are made to be broken, right? Nobody's watching anyway!""Zoning out is adult paradise!"Perfect vacation goals right here!Resting on the register, she savors a dream, tart and sweet.

223025.name: Sweet Invitation Melody
223025.desc: Material required for the Crescendo of specific Discs.
223025.literary: O little bunny,close your eyes and drift to sleep,I'll cradle you in the arms of the night;O little bunny,rest your head and dream sweetly,I promise you the sweetest treat of all.

223026.name: Vent It Out ♥ Melody
223026.desc: Material required for the Crescendo of specific Discs.
223026.literary: "La-la-la—welcome home, Master! ♥""Whether it's the weariness in your heart or the misfortune at your side,""I will personally help you sweep all that nasty trash away!""Let me turn my energy into your magic! ♥""Heaven's cutest maid, Beatrixa, at your service! ♥"With a clear, lively voice and an impossibly cute demeanor,she gave her all every dayto deliver healing and hope to her fans across the Nova Continent.

224001.name: Meowing Cat God Melody
224001.desc: Material required for the Crescendo of specific Discs.
224001.literary: Humans are born alone.Only in the heat of battle do we truly feel alive.Huh? Cool guys don't look at explosions? Fine, I heard you—

224002.name: Sky, Flowers, Poem Melody
224002.desc: Material required for the Crescendo of specific Discs.
224002.literary: Like flower petals, your departing form dissolves,Beneath starlit nights, our vows still warm my palm,These perfumed days bring thoughts of you, despite my own will.

224004.name: Wisteria Dream Melody
224004.desc: Material required for the Crescendo of specific Discs.
224004.literary: Look who's here—two little soft kittens on my knee?Afternoon tea time stretches far.Sleep soundly. Let purple wisteria shade your beautiful dreams.

224005.name: Sunlit Blossom Melody
224005.desc: Material required for the Crescendo of specific Discs.
224005.literary: The blossoms drift in rainy haze,That flowered in bright sunny days.A rainbow's gleam within my hand—Could such beauty ever stay?

224006.name: Witch's Swing Melody
224006.desc: Material required for the Crescendo of specific Discs.
224006.literary: The witch stands proud, head held high,Granting honey, venom, and love divine.You who failed to choose your princess right,Embrace this cruel pleasure, and dance with me tonight?

224007.name: Midnight Mayhem Melody
224007.desc: Material required for the Crescendo of specific Discs.
224007.literary: They set the rules of right and wrong,but if you loathe these bindings, rise as a midnight knight.Even if bloodied and broken, we're staying true to who we are!To those arrogant jerks:"See this mighty fist?""After the clock strikes twelve, this is our domain!"

224009.name: New Star Prelude Melody
224009.desc: Material required for the Crescendo of specific Discs.
224009.literary: Only one day of food left. Our wallets are empty. The Oasis's Grace is running low...We've staked everything on this Monolith commission...—Still, when it's time for the group photo, don't forget to smile!

224010.name: Prayer Beneath Light Melody
224010.desc: Material required for the Crescendo of specific Discs.
224010.literary: We beseech Thee, have mercy; heed our plea.Goddess, do the cries of mortals reach Thine ears?...—Each word finds Me, finds Us all.We shall guide humanity towards its glorious destiny.

224011.name: Summer Afternoon Rain Melody
224011.desc: Material required for the Crescendo of specific Discs.
224011.literary: Before looking back at the start, what seemed the end was justthe start of a new chapter.Are you happy as you've always dreamed you'd be?Let's meet again tomorrow.

224012.name: Predator's Gaze Melody
224012.desc: Material required for the Crescendo of specific Discs.
224012.literary: On United Harvest's grand design, Philae stands as just a single point.From here, I shall draw a perfect circle, claiming the entire Nova.—Follow me. Pledge loyalty. March ever onward.

224013.name: Voyage Map Melody
224013.desc: Material required for the Crescendo of specific Discs.
224013.literary: "First, we need a ship, then courage, and lastly, faith."The adventurer pinned the mapWhile whitecaps rage from point to pointWild waters crash and beckon towards mysteriesShe waits for kindred souls to sail.

224014.name: Sweet Times Melody
224014.desc: Material required for the Crescendo of specific Discs.
224014.literary: We trekked, picked, and laughed with our friends, sharing sweet fruit that burst with juice in our mouths.

224015.name: Deer's Song Melody
224015.desc: Material required for the Crescendo of specific Discs.
224015.literary: Deer call softly in the grove, wild grass their sweet feast.A maiden rests in afternoon shade, where sunbeams dance and weave.Like wind through time the moments flow, "Click"—a memory to keep.

224017.name: Fireworks Melody
224017.desc: Material required for the Crescendo of specific Discs.
224017.literary: Like a human life, fireworks bloom, flourish, and fade—brief yet brilliant, leaving their unique mark across the night sky.It's much like a Trekker's endless quest to climb the Monolith,all for that one day when they might finally hold the stars in their hands...

224018.name: Lemon & Black Tea Melody
224018.desc: Material required for the Crescendo of specific Discs.
224018.literary: With guilt my heart was heavy worn, to heal the bridge that had been torn.Thought friendship's door was closed for good,Till here we sit, just as we should.New décor graces these old walls, new packages the sweet food calls.One drink runs hot, one drink runs cold,Same taste remains from days of old.

224019.name: One Shot, One Down Melody
224019.desc: Material required for the Crescendo of specific Discs.
224019.literary: Kasimira, are you ready?This is round 37 and our final match for today.Too bad, just one shot shy.If that shot had landed, you'd have had me beat.Chaton, your hand wavered at the critical moment.Just the thought of besting you gets my adrenaline pumping!Let's do it again!Rack the gun, we've got the next commission to prep for.—Looks like Chaton's challenge isn't over yet.

224020.name: Sparkling Moment Melody
224020.desc: Material required for the Crescendo of specific Discs.
224020.literary: "Uneventful days aren't worth recording.""Dull little things aren't worth recording.""Repetitive work isn't worth recording."But ... are they truly worthless?A teammate's reminder before you head out, the wrong turn you took, the smiles and thanks you received...These ordinary fragments of memory condense into tiny points of light.Even if the paper turns yellow with time, the brilliance of each day will never be forgotten.

224021.name: United by Fate Melody
224021.desc: Material required for the Crescendo of specific Discs.
224021.literary: Friends, companions ... whatever the name, they all embody the same group of souls united by fate. They converge when the threads of fate intertwine, and disperse when they unwind.What we can do is cherish every fleeting moment of this reunion, laughing and playing with all our hearts, and etching those precious memories deep into our hearts.And as the hour of parting draws near, we cling to the hope of a future encounter, anticipating the day we shall meet again.

224022.name: The Meow Melody
224022.desc: Material required for the Crescendo of specific Discs.
224022.literary: Behold, something looms in the dark.Listen closely, do you hear those footsteps echoing?Odd, a sudden shiver runs down my spine.A faulty projector, an unknown film reel, and eerie visuals flickering...A Trekker's camp at midnight, an uninvited guest, and an unexpected visitor."Meow—"The silence envelops all. You close the door, but it has already slipped inside.

224023.name: Colors Pierce the Grey Melody
224023.desc: Material required for the Crescendo of specific Discs.
224023.literary: We had to take a day off now and then.Escape the gang fights and the daily grind,step out under a clear sky, and spray paint a rainbow of our own across it.

224024.name: One, Two, Three, Jump! Melody
224024.desc: Material required for the Crescendo of specific Discs.
224024.literary: A ropedangled from a sunlit ledge,dropping into the long-forgotten ruins.The girl grabbed itand rappelled down."Hah, just some treasure?Watch me haul it up!"

224026.name: Sword Against Stream Melody
224026.desc: Material required for the Crescendo of specific Discs.
224026.literary: Damp hair clung to her back.Her clothes were a mess, yet the air was stiflingly still.Carrying a heavy heart, even the falling petals seemed to weigh her down.As the rain fell endlessly, your silhouette began to blur.

224027.name: Dragon-Phoenix Melody
224027.desc: Material required for the Crescendo of specific Discs.
224027.literary: Brush and ink are her weapons.On the stretched rice paper,She weaves her magic, each brushstroke dancing in unconventional places.This is her realm, a world of enchantment solely under her command.

224028.name: Daylight Garden Melody
224028.desc: Material required for the Crescendo of specific Discs.
224028.literary: A petal without a name or numberdrifts into the silent garden,carrying a blush of crimson and a vision of pure white,settling into a golden specimen, alongside a vanished dream.

224030.name: A Moment in the Afternoon Melody
224030.desc: Material required for the Crescendo of specific Discs.
224030.literary: The girl burst in with the afternoon sun,bringing with her the aroma of snacks.Fries? Grilled fish? Or a loaf of fluffy, warm bread?You had to grab somethingto enjoy this stolen moment of peace.

224031.name: The Clash of Blade and Axe Melody
224031.desc: Material required for the Crescendo of specific Discs.
224031.literary: An alarm blared as blade met axe.The cage shattered, and she plunged into the abyss.Through the crimson rain, she met your eyes.

224032.name: Dream Factory of ☆ Truth Melody
224032.desc: Material required for the Crescendo of specific Discs.
224032.literary: Facts captured.Photos printed.Story broadcast.Welcome to the witches' Truth ☆ Dream Factory!

224033.name: Dancing with the Bones Melody
224033.desc: Material required for the Crescendo of specific Discs.
224033.literary: Ah, welcome to my ball, my dear patient.Listen, the music is playing. Come, dance with my collection among these phantom bubbles.

224036.name: The Lost Pilgrim Melody
224036.desc: Material required for the Crescendo of specific Discs.
224036.literary: Body bound, soul eroded,even pain masquerades as a mire of salvation.The fallen priestess still wanderson a pilgrimage with no answers and no end,awaiting a righteous one to grant her release.

224037.name: Claw the Claw Melody
224037.desc: Material required for the Crescendo of specific Discs.
224037.literary: The children of the Ash District tell a legend:when despair grips the world and tears loved ones apart,a green-haired heroine called the "Lord of the Prize Claw" and her brave companionswill lead everyone to catch the last glimmer of hope and reunite with their families.

224038.name: Ripples of Nostalgia Melody
224038.desc: Material required for the Crescendo of specific Discs.
224038.literary: Floating on a thousand crests,a translucent, shimmering thing.Escaping the searing summer heat,drifting along with the migrating fish.

224039.name: Summer Sanctuary Melody
224039.desc: Material required for the Crescendo of specific Discs.
224039.literary: I long for the sea breeze to linger, for the waves to remain.I pray for the sunset to stretch endlessly, for the starlight to never fade.I wish to share with you alone—a summer that belongs to us.

224040.name: Fist of Courage Melody
224040.desc: Material required for the Crescendo of specific Discs.
224040.literary: To protect your companions, to summon the courage and become your best self,strike your fist at the colossal enemy,and clear the path to a future full of hope.

224041.name: A Gift for the Journey Melody
224041.desc: Material required for the Crescendo of specific Discs.
224041.literary: A sleigh full of giftsguided by the messengerheading toward the sunrise and its destinationexcept—shouldn't reindeer be pulling it?!

224043.name: The Bud of Change Melody
224043.desc: Material required for the Crescendo of specific Discs.
224043.literary: Beneath soil steeped in conspiracy and intrigue,Watchful, calculating gazes interweave.Something is struggling to break through the earth.

224048.name: Snowy Night Surprise Melody
224048.desc: Material required for the Crescendo of specific Discs.
224048.literary: The winter wind carries prayers from afarThe messenger arrives with blessings and giftsstepping into view as the midnight bells ringThis Snowish Festival gift is for you, who never lost your childish wonder

511712.name: Neutral Left, Live Right, Ground Below

514123.name: Sigil Unleashed: Tiger of the East

514124.name: Tiger of the East: Blazing Scales
